21static inline isc_result_t
22fromtext_zonemd(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
23 isc_token_t token;
24 int digest_type, length;
25
26 UNUSED(type);
27 UNUSED(rdclass);
28 UNUSED(origin);
29 UNUSED(options);
30 UNUSED(callbacks);
31
32 /*
33 * Serial.
34 */
35 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
36 false));
37 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
38
39 /*
40 * Digest type.
41 */
42 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
43 false));
44 digest_type = token.value.as_ulong;
45 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(digest_type, target));
46
47 /*
48 * Reserved.
49 */
50 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
51 false));
52 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
53
54 /*
55 * Digest.
56 */
57 switch (digest_type) {
58 case DNS_ZONEMD_DIGEST_SHA384:
59 length = ISC_SHA384_DIGESTLENGTH;
60 break;
61 default:
62 length = -2;
63 break;
64 }
65
66 return (isc_hex_tobuffer(lexer, target, length));
67}
68
69static inline isc_result_t
70totext_zonemd(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
71 isc_region_t sr;
72 char buf[sizeof("0123456789")];
73 unsigned long num;
74
75 REQUIRE(rdata->length > 6);
76
77 UNUSED(tctx);
78
79 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
80
81 /*
82 * Serial.
83 */
84 num = uint32_fromregion(&sr);
85 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
86 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%lu", num);
87 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
88
89 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
90
91 /*
92 * Digest type.
93 */
94 num = uint8_fromregion(&sr);
95 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
96 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%lu", num);
97 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
98
99 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
100 /*
101 * Reserved.
102 */
103 num = uint8_fromregion(&sr);
104 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
105 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%lu", num);
106 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
107
108 /*
109 * Digest.
110 */
111 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
112 RETERR(str_totext(" (", target));
113 RETERR(str_totext(tctx->linebreak, target));
114 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_NOCRYPTO) == 0) {
115 if (tctx->width == 0) /* No splitting */
116 RETERR(isc_hex_totext(&sr, 0, "", target));
117 else
118 RETERR(isc_hex_totext(&sr, tctx->width - 2,
119 tctx->linebreak, target));
120 } else {
121 RETERR(str_totext("[omitted]", target));
122 }
123 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0) {
124 RETERR(str_totext(" )", target));
125 }
126 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
127}

129static inline isc_result_t
130fromwire_zonemd(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
131 isc_region_t sr;
132
133 UNUSED(type);
134 UNUSED(rdclass);
135 UNUSED(dctx);
136 UNUSED(options);
137
138 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sr);
139
140 /*
141 * If we do not recognize the digest type, only ensure that the digest
142 * is present at all.
143 *
144 * If we do recognize the digest type, ensure that the digest is of the
145 * correct length.
146 */
147 if (sr.length < 7 ||
148 (sr.base[4] == DNS_ZONEMD_DIGEST_SHA384 &&
149 sr.length < 6 + ISC_SHA384_DIGESTLENGTH))
150 {
151 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
152 }
153
154 /*
155 * Only specify the number of octets to consume if we recognize the
156 * digest type.
157 *
158 * If there is extra data, dns_rdata_fromwire() will detect that.
159 */
160 if (sr.base[4] == DNS_ZONEMD_DIGEST_SHA384) {
161 sr.length = 6 + ISC_SHA384_DIGESTLENGTH;
162 }
163
164 isc_buffer_forward(source, sr.length);
165 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
166}

168static inline isc_result_t
169towire_zonemd(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
170 isc_region_t sr;
171
172 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_zonemd);
173 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
174
175 UNUSED(cctx);
176
177 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
178 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
179}

181static inline int
182compare_zonemd(ARGS_COMPARE) {
183 isc_region_t r1;
184 isc_region_t r2;
185
186 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
187 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
188 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_zonemd);
189 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
190 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
191
192 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
193 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
194 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
195}
196
197static inline isc_result_t
198fromstruct_zonemd(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
199 dns_rdata_zonemd_t *zonemd = source;
200
201 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
202 REQUIRE(zonemd->common.rdtype == type);
203 REQUIRE(zonemd->common.rdclass == rdclass);
204
205 UNUSED(type);
206 UNUSED(rdclass);
207
208 switch (zonemd->digest_type) {
209 case DNS_ZONEMD_DIGEST_SHA384:
210 REQUIRE(zonemd->length == ISC_SHA384_DIGESTLENGTH);
211 break;
212 }
213
214 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(zonemd->serial, target));
215 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(zonemd->digest_type, target));
216 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(zonemd->reserved, target));
217
218 return (mem_tobuffer(target, zonemd->digest, zonemd->length));
219}
220
221static inline isc_result_t
222tostruct_zonemd(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
223 dns_rdata_zonemd_t *zonemd = target;
224 isc_region_t region;
225
226 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_zonemd);
227 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
228 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
229
230 zonemd->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
231 zonemd->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
232 ISC_LINK_INIT(&zonemd->common, link);
233
234 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
235
236 zonemd->serial = uint32_fromregion(&region);
237 isc_region_consume(&region, 4);
238 zonemd->digest_type = uint8_fromregion(&region);
239 isc_region_consume(&region, 1);
240 zonemd->reserved = uint8_fromregion(&region);
241 isc_region_consume(&region, 1);
242 zonemd->length = region.length;
243
244 zonemd->digest = mem_maybedup(mctx, region.base, region.length);
245 if (zonemd->digest == NULL) {
246 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
247 }
248
249 zonemd->mctx = mctx;
250 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
251}
252
253static inline void
254freestruct_zonemd(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
255 dns_rdata_zonemd_t *zonemd = source;
256
257 REQUIRE(zonemd != NULL);
258 REQUIRE(zonemd->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_zonemd);
259
260 if (zonemd->mctx == NULL) {
261 return;
262 }
263
264 if (zonemd->digest != NULL) {
265 isc_mem_free(zonemd->mctx, zonemd->digest);
266 }
267 zonemd->mctx = NULL;
268}

274 UNUSED(rdata);

281static inline isc_result_t
282digest_zonemd(ARGS_DIGEST) {
283 isc_region_t r;
284
285 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_zonemd);
286
287 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
288
289 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
290}
